        <num>CC 2901</num>
        <heading>2901.  Retaking before or after conclusion of use or expiration of time</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2901.  Retaking before or after conclusion of use or expiration of time
The lender may demand the return of the thing lent after expiration of the term and, in the absence of a term, after conclusion of the use for which the thing was lent.  In case of urgent and unforeseen need, the lender may demand the return of the thing at any time.</p>
        </content>
